msgid "Juli's dismembered body."
msgstr "ジュリの切断された遺体。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K5.chr_juli.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "What...?"
msgstr "どうして……？"

msgid "This can't be..."
msgstr "そんなはずない……"

msgid "Kaya's lifeless body."
msgstr "カヤの遺体。"

msgid "Oh my god."
msgstr "そんなはずない……"

msgid "She didn't deserve this..."
msgstr "こんな目に遭うべき子じゃないのに……"

msgid "Saki's headless body."
msgstr "首を斬られたサキの遺体。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Ending_K5.chr_saki.dlg.kat"
msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "No way... this can't be real..."
msgstr "そんなはずない……こんなの、現実のはずない……"

msgid "A school desk."
msgstr "学校の机。"

msgid "It feels unnatural to the touch, like it's made of stone."
msgstr "手触りが不自然で、石で出来ているかのようだ。"

msgid "Wait...!"
msgstr "その前に……！"
